data.description: Pride of home ownership is shown throughout the home. No Deferred Maintenace Needed here! New AC 2022, New Windows, Sliders & Doors 2018 & 2021, New Garage Door 2014, partial newer vinyl fencing, 2021 Generac generator system and a newer Dimensional Roof 2012. This is a Very spacious home with over 1959 sq. ft 3 bedrooms on a large corner lot. Some of the features include a Gas fireplace, Granite Countertops, Newer Stainless appliances, modern open kitchen perfect for family get togethers & entertaining, raised glass bowl sinks in bathrooms, inside laundry & tub, living dining combo and eat in kitchen dining area. Did I mention it has a one-of-a-kind Luxury wooden door and a screen enclosed Lania & more!
